{
  "stem": "3685.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 1936, in that particular town of Berestechko, that was a-- that was already maybe-- over there it could be about 500 or 600 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, so there, in 1936-- I remember when I went to school in '37, '38-- was big transprints-- don't buy at the Jews; Jews to Palestine-- such a thing, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was in '36, and '37, and '38, up to till the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- that was-- I remember, I used to go there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It used to be big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't buy at Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Jews, go to Palestine, and, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Nazis-- from the papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I actually knew in '34 or '35.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know, you know, what they were actually-- but we knew this-- the Nazis, because in-- in Lemberg, we had a university.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two Jews were killed in the-- on the campuses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, you know, and we knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of the Jews we knew, because he had a-- he was a big landowner near us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his son-- that was his son who got killed on the campus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, I remember, the paper wrote that's all blowing over from Germany, from Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The papers wrote that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Polish and the Jewish press wrote that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember reading in the paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- Do you remember his name?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- it's Zellemier Yeah, I remember well his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were a family-- actually, they were very rich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the sons went to the Spanish-- you know when the Spanish war was on?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he went to fight on the-- on the left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And his father was a-- a millionaire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, when-- when the Russians came in in 1939, they name a street by the name Zellemier-- is-- you want me to spell it?",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
